        <div class="observation__date">February, 2017</div>
        <div class="observation__author">Ronnie Demientieff</div>
        <div class="observation__description">
          <p>Open water in February. Froze to the bottom, then flooded over because of lack of snow (no insulation). This can be dangerous and hard for snow machine travel. It's hard on machines and I had to find a route around.  This change affects trapping. I first started noticing this change in 2011, but not observe it seasonally. It has a strong effect on safety.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
