        <a name="ice-conditions-observation-4"></a>
        <div class="observation__date">March 4, 2016</div>
        <div class="observation__author">Dean Painter</div>
        <div class="observation__description">
          <p>Open water in snowmachine trail on way to check beaver sets going toward Kaiyuh. Open all the way across, makes snow machine access dangerous. This change effects trapping, happens seasonally, is observed often, and has a moderate affect on safety.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
